      state taxes, and many credits and deductions. Real tax situations are
      often more complex than any calculator can model.
    </p>

    <h2>Tax Law Changes</h2>
    <p>
      Federal tax brackets, standard deductions, and credits change. We update
      the calculators regularly, but at any given moment they may reflect rules
      from the most recently completed tax year rather than the current one.
      Verify current numbers on
      <a href='https://www.irs.gov' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>irs.gov</a>
